Package mksinterface.query.src

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Mksinterface_query
    Class for creating, handling and executing a mksquery
    Mksinterface_query_option
    This class saves a Option for a query INFO: This class is not used for the moment I need it for a future query implementation
    Mksinterface_query_optionList
    This class saves all options of the query like a list.
    Mksinterface_result
    Class which parses the response object which is given from the interface and provide all different items for the user Attention: This class do not check if the data is valid.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    Mksinterface_executeQueryException
    Exception which occurs if the execution of the query fails
    Mksinterface_parseResultException
    Exception occurs if parsing the Response to a result failed
